PN,37205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F372A1772283793
OL,3,CDriver left with #1,500 bill after
OL,4,Cpotholes damage wheels
OL,6,FThe incident is said to have taken
OL,7,Fplace on Thursday, February 12, near
OL,8,Fthe Meadows Community Centre on Slant
OL,9,FLane in Mansfield Woodhouse.
OL,11,FThe victim, a man in his 40s from
OL,12,FDerby was taken to the King's Mill
OL,13,FHospital by an ambulance.
OL,15,FThe extent of his injuries are not yet
OL,16,Fknown.
OL,18,FWatch on ITVX: Potholes & Pile-ups: A
OL,19,Fspecial programme looking at the state
OL,20,Fof the roads in the Midlands
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G5/5
